{"id":1722,"date":"2018-11-20T22:04:55","date_gmt":"2018-11-21T03:04:55","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/mossiso.com\/?p=1722"},"modified":"2018-11-20T22:04:55","modified_gmt":"2018-11-21T03:04:55","slug":"making-the-best-use-of-your-time","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/mossiso.com\/2018\/11\/20\/making-the-best-use-of-your-time\/","title":{"rendered":"Making the BEST use of your time."},"content":{"rendered":"<p>I have been reading several books lately that are encouraging me to use my time wisely and helping me realize I can accomplish whatever I want to do.<\/p>\n<p>My wife is also starting up a life coaching business soon, <a href=\"http:\/\/jessicashepherd.coach\">http:\/\/jessicashepherd.coach<\/a>, and all of this has got me thinking of ways for me to improve on a daily business.<\/p>\n<p>For about a year now, I have been tracking things I want to do to improve. I have a journal that I write in nearly daily. At the beginning of each month, I decide on a few things that I want to focus on for the month, draw a little chart, and track those things each day.<\/p>\n<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-1722 gallery-columns-2 gallery-size-medium'><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https:\/\/mossiso.com\/2018\/11\/20\/making-the-best-use-of-your-time\/img_20181120_214139\/'><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"163\" src=\"https:\/\/mossiso.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/IMG_20181120_214139-300x163.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mossiso.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/IMG_20181120_214139-300x163.jpg 300w, https:\/\/mossiso.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/IMG_20181120_214139-768x417.jpg 768w, https:\/\/mossiso.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/IMG_20181120_214139-1024x556.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/mossiso.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/IMG_20181120_214139-150x81.jpg 150w, https:\/\/mossiso.com\/wp-conten