 for the &#8220;O&#8221;, so I came up with the next best thing; BEST, as in make the BEST of each day. Each letter stands for something to focus on each day.<\/p>\n<p>B = brain. Do something to make you smarter.<\/p>\n<p>E = exercise. Work your body.<\/p>\n<p>S = spiritual. Do something to get closer to God.<\/p>\n<p>T = talent. Do something to improve an existing talent or start learning a new one.<\/p>\n<p>So this month, to make each day the BEST, I&#8217;m working on<a href=\"http:\/\/mossiso.com\/2018\/11\/20\/making-the-best-use-of-your-time.html\/img_20181120_214430\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-1734\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-1734\" src=\"http:\/\/mossiso.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/IMG_20181120_214430-300x215.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"215\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mossiso.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/IMG_20181120_214430-300x215.jpg 300w, https:\/\/mossiso.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/IMG_20181120_214430-768x550.jpg 768w, https:\/\/mossiso.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/IMG_20181120_214430-1024x733.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/mossiso.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/IMG_20181120_214430-150x107.jpg 150w, https:\/\/mossiso.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/IMG_20181120_214430-624x447.jpg 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>B = brain: reading The Success Principles by Jack Canfield and Janet Switzer<\/p>\n<p>E = exercise: give 100% when running, stretching, and 100 pushups program<\/p>\n<p>S = spiritual: read from the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.lds.org\/ensign\/2018\/11?lang=eng\">Ensign<\/a><\/p>\n<p>T = talent: write a book. I have always wanted to write a sci-fi or fantasy book, so I am!<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>You can also see that I&#8217;m trying to be creative with lettering the month and year, and the design for filling in each days box, and miserably failing. Perhaps that will be a talent goal for a future month&#8230;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n